    public interface ModelPart
extends MappingModelExpressable
    Describes a mapping related to any part of the app's domain model - e.g. an attribute, an entity identifier, collection elements, etc
    See Also:
    DomainResultProducer, todo (6.0) : do we need to expose ModelPartContainer here? Only if _necessary_
